.SH NAME
atmel_lcdfb_alloc_video_memory \- Allocate framebuffer memory
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" atmel_lcdfb_alloc_video_memory
.BI "(struct atmel_lcdfb_info *sinfo "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "sinfo" 12
the frame buffer to allocate memory for

This function is called only from the \fBatmel_lcdfb_probe\fP
so no locking by fb_info->mm_lock around smem_len setting is needed.
